<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Protocolo de Competição — SBBSF</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --azul: #0D2A5E; --azul2: #1A3F80; --amarelo: #F5C500; --verde: #009933;
  --vermelho: #C0392B; --laranja: #E67E22; --cinza: #F0F3F8; --borda: #DDE3EE;
  --texto: #1A1A2E; --muted: #6B7A99; --teal: #0D8C7A;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: #F7F9FD; color: var(--texto); min-height: 100vh; }
header { background: var(--azul); padding: 0; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(13,42,94,0.18); }
.header-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; }
.header-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.header-badge { background: var(--amarelo); color: var(--azul); font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; }
.header-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; color: #fff; line-height: 1.2; }
.header-sub { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-weight: 300; }
.btn-voltar { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 14px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; }
.hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #071A2B 0%, #0D2A5E 60%, #1A3F80 100%); padding: 32px 24px; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--amarelo); }
.hero-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
.hero-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: var(--amarelo); color: var(--azul); font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 99px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.hero-titulo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 26px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.2; }
.hero-sub { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hstat { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 18px; text-align: center; }
.hstat-num { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; color: var(--amarelo); line-height: 1; }
.hstat-label { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-top: 2px; }
.hooper-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 28px auto; padding: 0 24px; }
.section-titulo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 16px; color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.section-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.hooper-card { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid var(--borda); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(13,42,94,0.07); }
.hooper-header { background: var(--azul); padding: 14px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.hooper-header-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #fff; }
.hooper-header-sub { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top: 1px; }
.hooper-body { padding: 20px; }
.hooper-inputs { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
@media(max-width:480px){ .hooper-inputs { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.hooper-field .field-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.slider-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.hooper-slider { flex: 1; -webkit-appearance: none; height: 6px; border-radius: 3px; outline: none; cursor: pointer; background: #E5E7EB; }
.hooper-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb { -webkit-appearance: none; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--azul); cursor: pointer; border: 2px solid #fff; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
.slider-val { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; color: var(--azul); min-width: 28px; text-align: center; }
.slider-labels { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
.btn-calcular { width: 100%; background: var(--azul); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 13px; font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.btn-calcular:hover { background: var(--azul2); }
.resultado-hooper { display: none; margin-top: 16px; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 2px solid; }
.resultado-hooper.verde { border-color: #009933; background: #F0FFF4; }
.resultado-hooper.amarelo { border-color: #E8A020; background: #FFFBEB; }
.resultado-hooper.vermelho { border-color: #C0392B; background: #FFF5F5; }
.resultado-header { padding: 12px 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.resultado-hooper.verde .resultado-header { background: #009933; }
.resultado-hooper.amarelo .resultado-header { background: #E8A020; }
.resultado-hooper.vermelho .resultado-header { background: #C0392B; }
.resultado-emoji { font-size: 22px; }
.resultado-titulo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px; color: #fff; }
.resultado-score { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-top: 1px; }
.resultado-body { padding: 14px 18px; }
.resultado-protocolo { font-size: 13px; color: var(--texto); line-height: 1.6; }
.resultado-protocolo strong { color: var(--azul); }
.resultado-alerta { margin-top: 10px; background: rgba(13,42,94,0.06); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }
.timeline-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 28px; padding: 0 24px; }
.timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
.tl-item { display: flex; gap: 0; position: relative; }
.tl-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; width: 64px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.tl-hora { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; color: var(--azul); text-align: center; padding-top: 18px; line-height: 1.1; }
.tl-hora small { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); display: block; }
.tl-line-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding-top: 18px; }
.tl-dot { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2.5px solid #fff; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px currentColor; }
.tl-line { width: 2px; flex: 1; min-height: 20px; }
.tl-right { flex: 1; padding: 14px 0 14px 16px; }
.tl-card { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid var(--borda); border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px 18px; transition: box-shadow 0.2s; }
.tl-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(13,42,94,0.10); }
.tl-card-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.tl-card-icon { font-size: 20px; }
.tl-card-titulo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: var(--azul); flex: 1; line-height: 1.3; }
.tl-card-badge { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 99px; white-space: nowrap; }
.tl-card-lista { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
.tl-item-ex { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--texto); line-height: 1.5; }
.tl-num { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 10px; color: var(--amarelo); background: var(--azul); border-radius: 50%; width: 16px; height: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
.tl-obs { margin-top: 10px; background: #FFF8E1; border-left: 3px solid var(--amarelo); border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #7A5C00; font-weight: 500; }
.tl-item-jogo .tl-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #071A2B, #0D2A5E); border-color: var(--amarelo); }
.tl-item-jogo .tl-card-titulo { color: #fff; }
.tl-item-jogo .tl-card-top { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.jogo-info { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.jogo-stat { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 14px; text-align: center; }
.jogo-stat-label { font-size: 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; display: block; }
.jogo-stat-val { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; color: var(--amarelo); display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
.jogo-texto { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-top: 12px; line-height: 1.6; }
.semaforo-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 28px; padding: 0 24px; }
.semaforo-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; }
@media(max-width:600px){ .semaforo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.semaforo-card { border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; border: 2px solid; }
.semaforo-card.verde { border-color: #009933; }
.semaforo-card.amarelo { border-color: #E8A020; }
.semaforo-card.vermelho { border-color: #C0392B; }
.semaforo-top { padding: 12px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.semaforo-card.verde .semaforo-top { background: #009933; }
.semaforo-card.amarelo .semaforo-top { background: #E8A020; }
.semaforo-card.vermelho .semaforo-top { background: #C0392B; }
.semaforo-circulo { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.semaforo-card.verde .semaforo-circulo { background: #00CC44; }
.semaforo-card.amarelo .semaforo-circulo { background: #FFD700; }
.semaforo-card.vermelho .semaforo-circulo { background: #E74C3C; }
.semaforo-titulo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; color: #fff; line-height: 1.2; }
.semaforo-score { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
.semaforo-body { padding: 14px 16px; background: #fff; }
.semaforo-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 6px; display: block; }
.semaforo-item { font-size: 12px; color: var(--texto); line-height: 1.6; padding: 4px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cinza); }
.semaforo-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.semaforo-item strong { color: var(--azul); }
.btb-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 28px; padding: 0 24px; }
.btb-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D0A0A, #5C1A1A); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; border: 2px solid #C0392B; }
.btb-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; background: #C0392B; color: #fff; font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 3px 12px; border-radius: 99px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.btb-titulo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.btb-sub { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6; }
.btb-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
@media(max-width:520px){ .btb-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.btb-bloco { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
.btb-bloco-titulo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; color: var(--amarelo); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.btb-lista { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
.btb-item { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: 7px; }
.btb-item::before { content: "→"; color: var(--amarelo); flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 700; }
.btb-alerta { margin-top: 16px; background: rgba(192,57,43,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.5); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #FFB3B3; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6; }
.btb-alerta strong { color: #fff; }
.wa-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 28px; padding: 0 24px; }
.wa-card { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid var(--borda); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; }
.wa-header { background: #25D366; padding: 14px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.wa-header-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #fff; }
.wa-header-sub { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
.wa-body { padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
.wa-msg { background: #DCF8C6; border-radius: 12px 12px 12px 2px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #1A1A2E; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 90%; position: relative; }
.wa-msg::before { content: attr(data-horario); display: block; font-size: 10px; color: #6B7A99; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.wa-msg-titulo { font-weight: 700; color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.wa-copy { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: var(--cinza); border: 1px solid var(--borda); border-radius: 8px; padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; margin-top: 8px; transition: all 0.15s; }
.wa-copy:hover { background: var(--azul); color: #fff; border-color: var(--azul); }
footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--borda); padding: 20px 32px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; margin-top: 40px; }
footer strong { color: var(--azul); font-style: normal; }
.cor-manha { color: #E8A020; }
.cor-prejogo { color: #0D8C7A; }
.cor-posjogo { color: #1A6B9A; }
.cor-noite { color: #7B2D8B; }
.bg-manha { background: #FFF8E1; border-color: #E8A020 !important; }
.bg-prejogo { background: #E0F7F4; border-color: #0D8C7A !important; }
.bg-noite { background: #F5F0FF; border-color: #7B2D8B !important; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-brand">
      <div class="header-badge">BeachMed</div>
      <div>
        <div class="header-title">Protocolo de Competição Remota</div>
        <div class="header-sub">Seleção Brasileira Feminina de Beach Soccer</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="./index.html" class="btn-voltar">← Banco de Exercícios</a>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-tag">🏆 Gestão Remota de Carga</div>
    <div class="hero-titulo">Dia de Jogo — O que fazer e quando</div>
    <div class="hero-sub">Protocolo autônomo para atletas em competição. Consulte o Hooper da manhã, identifique sua zona e siga o protocolo do dia. A Gabi monitora os dados remotamente.</div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-num">3</div><div class="hstat-label">Momentos</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-num">1 jogo</div><div class="hstat-label">por dia</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-num">Hooper</div><div class="hstat-label">decide o protocolo</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-num">18 min</div><div class="hstat-label">pré-jogo</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="hooper-section">
  <div class="section-titulo">📊 Checador de Hooper — Manhã do Jogo</div>
  <div class="section-sub">Preencha logo ao acordar. O resultado define o seu protocolo de hoje.</div>
  <div class="hooper-card">
    <div class="hooper-header">
      <div>
        <div class="hooper-header-title">Índice de Hooper</div>
        <div class="hooper-header-sub">1 = ótimo &nbsp;|&nbsp; 7 = péssimo — responda com honestidade</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hooper-body">
      <div class="hooper-inputs">
        <div class="hooper-field">
          <div class="field-name">😴 Qualidade do Sono</div>
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input type="range" min="1" max="7" value="3" class="hooper-slider" id="sl-sono" oninput="atualizarSlider('sono',this.value)">
            <div class="slider-val" id="val-sono">3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-labels"><span>Ótimo</span><span>Péssimo</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hooper-field">
          <div class="field-name">😰 Nível de Estresse</div>
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input type="range" min="1" max="7" value="3" class="hooper-slider" id="sl-estresse" oninput="atualizarSlider('estresse',this.value)">
            <div class="slider-val" id="val-estresse">3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-labels"><span>Nenhum</span><span>Muito alto</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hooper-field">
          <div class="field-name">💪 Fadiga Física</div>
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input type="range" min="1" max="7" value="3" class="hooper-slider" id="sl-fadiga" oninput="atualizarSlider('fadiga',this.value)">
            <div class="slider-val" id="val-fadiga">3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-labels"><span>Descansada</span><span>Exausta</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hooper-field">
          <div class="field-name">🦵 Dor Muscular</div>
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input type="range" min="1" max="7" value="3" class="hooper-slider" id="sl-dor" oninput="atualizarSlider('dor',this.value)">
            <div class="slider-val" id="val-dor">3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-labels"><span>Nenhuma</span><span>Intensa</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-calcular" onclick="calcularHooper()">Calcular meu protocolo de hoje →</button>
      <div class="resultado-hooper" id="resultado-hooper">
        <div class="resultado-header">
          <div class="resultado-emoji" id="res-emoji"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="resultado-titulo" id="res-titulo"></div>
            <div class="resultado-score" id="res-score"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resultado-body">
          <div class="resultado-protocolo" id="res-protocolo"></div>
          <div class="resultado-alerta" id="res-alerta"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div><div class="timeline-section">
  <div class="section-titulo">🕐 Rotina Completa do Dia de Jogo</div>
  <div class="section-sub">Horários baseados em jogo às 15h — ajuste proporcionalmente ao horário do seu jogo.</div>
  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-left">
        <div class="tl-hora">7h<small>manhã</small></div>
        <div class="tl-line-wrap">
          <div class="tl-dot" style="color:#E8A020"></div>
          <div class="tl-line" style="background:linear-gradient(#E8A020,#E8A02044)"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-right">
        <div class="tl-card bg-manha">
          <div class="tl-card-top">
            <div class="tl-card-icon">☀️</div>
            <div class="tl-card-titulo cor-manha">Acordar — Hooper + Nutrição</div>
            <div class="tl-card-badge" style="background:#FFF3CD;color:#856404">Obrigatório</div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-card-lista">
            <div class="tl-item-ex"><span class="tl-num">1</span><span><strong>Preencher o Hooper</strong> no formulário (link no grupo) — faça antes de se levantar da cama se possível</span></div>
            <div class="tl-item-ex"><span class="tl-num">2</span><span><strong>Café da manhã reforçado:</strong> carboidrato + proteína + fruta. Não pular. Comer até 3h antes do jogo.</span></div>
            <div class="tl-item-ex"><span class="tl-num">3</span><span><strong>Hidratação:</strong> 500ml de água ao acordar. Meta do dia: 35ml/kg de peso corporal.</span></div>
            <div class="tl-item-ex"><span class="tl-num">4</span><span><strong>Autoavaliação:</strong> alguma dor nova em relação a ontem? Reportar para a Gabi pelo WhatsApp.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-obs">⚠️ Se o Hooper total for ≥ 20, avise a Gabi imediatamente — o protocolo pré-jogo será adaptado.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-left">
        <div class="tl-hora">12h<small>meio-dia</small></div>
        <div class="tl-line-wrap">
          <div class="tl-dot" style="color:#0D8C7A"></div>
          <div class="tl-line" style="background:linear-gradient(#0D8C7A,#0D8C7A44)"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
